value.0: With their flaming wings and skull-like countenance, these demons are among the greatest and most feared of their kind.
Though not true Dire creatures, these Spiders are nevertheless fearsome to behold and appear to act with more cunning than their more common cousins.
Friends of the Drow, the Underdark Spiders live in harmony with Drow by helping out with security and eliminating other vermin.

While Goblins are often considered little more than a nuisance, an unchecked population can often balloon into a serious threat to normally civilized areas.
The biggest and strongest of the goblinoids, Bugbears receive their name from their bear-like noses, strong upper body, and keen sense of smell.
